highlights.text: Tobias Rahim has the most spots on Top Songs Denmark. “Elsker når du smiler” is the highest at #4.
“Dark Room (feat. ICEKIID)” by Tobias Rahim and ICEKIID is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Denmark, up 104 spots at #56.
“Reposado” by Benny Jamz and Gilli has been on Top Songs Denmark the longest, at 456 days straight.
“Sandheden” by Rasmus Seebach and Artigeardit is the highest new entry on Top Songs Denmark at #1.
